{"tid":469894,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實果邊咪有電話亭個電視廣告都幾成功","createTime":"2017-11-15T18:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T05:24:56.000Z","uid":18299,"like":248,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"fe1d185956d37d244e91299ab28a303cc51cf67f","tid":469894,"uid":18299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T18:56:15.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n早兩日係地鐵站等緊朋友黎 <br />\n佢話下站就會到 而且仲係咁打比我 <br />\n但部電話無喇喇touch唔到<br />\n我先問港鐵職員佢地話無帶電話係身<br />\n叫我問服務中心 但服務台又話內線打唔到岀去 叫我搵電話亭<br />\n但我怕行開左 朋友又到我見佢唔到 <br />\n所以又去左車站鋪頭借電話 點知都係叫我搵服務中心 <br />\n咁眼見朋友係咁打黎 <br />\n我最後打算問路人借電話 無一個人願意借 即刻走開左<br />\n果刻其實失落多過憤怒 明明真係有需要 但個個以為我騙子咁 <br />\n到底係廣告既成功<br />\n定係香港太多騙子 令到人怕左幫人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f131341af27c16bb61c2576f819cff0813c3c5","tid":469894,"uid":82963,"like":178,"dislike":2,"score":176,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T18:58:03.000Z","msg":"你個樣嚇親人喇"},{"pid":"8a6cb501ce0566625a1dee3b6c0aeb47158e4a90","tid":469894,"uid":18299,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T18:59:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個樣嚇親人喇</blockquote><br />\n可能喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6c21a28f9cb56ba900f3f9536781c90f82ba7b4","tid":469894,"uid":18299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T19:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"762ccbc8c6eaf6abdbf7955d620c1aadb6800128","tid":469894,"uid":18299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T19:06:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6722ed7bab56d0f3f3feef1671efc4b81a332bf","tid":469894,"uid":18299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T19:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b8ab34622b7f37f5ab04f19d62f484dd79266c9","tid":469894,"uid":18299,"like":0,"dislike":1,"sc